    "description": "When Master left the atelier, Riblo, an alchemist, suddenly began to stand alone.<br><br>Riblo explores new places Meet various people, She comes across multiple experiences.<br>To Riblo, who has never been outside the Pipi Forest, The outside world is full of new and mysterious things.<br>Will Riblo be able to safely make &quot;Philosopher's Stone&quot; and solve Master's homework?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/c238f78cd5fe00b5c5f2fc4c8436e4ea.poster.avif?t=1743424779\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/c238f78cd5fe00b5c5f2fc4c8436e4ea.webm?t=1743424779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/c238f78cd5fe00b5c5f2fc4c8436e4ea.mp4?t=1743424779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>【Alchemy using the Alchemy Pot】<br>Riblo is an alchemist who can collect various ingredients and combine items<br>in the alchemy pot.<br>The combined item can be used for the residents who need help by progressing the episode<br>or receiving a quest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/f88c4347236d040362d8cf79bdc96620.avif?t=1743424779\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br>【Collect various materials】<br>Riblo explores various locations and collects new materials.<br>She may sometimes need alchemy-made items to get the ingredients she wants.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/bc03070717ee7da695a16d5370acd045.avif?t=1743424779\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br>【Resolving requests from residents】<br>Riblo can solve quests with items made with alchemy.<br>Check out the Quest notes of residents in need on the town board of Pipi Town!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/ce4eccecc1c1c8196676469bdf9b522f.avif?t=1743424779\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br>【Collect Alchemy Recipe】<br>Riblo can complete the recipe book by registering alchemy recipes.<br>Recipes can be purchased at the Pipi Town Recipe Store.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587240/extras/00c435b1e6db69539a482da74db52f29.avif?t=1743424779\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br>【Various episodes】<br>NPC of various races appear in the Alchemist of Pipi Forest.<br>Residents ask for help from Riblo and sometimes help Riblo.<br>Various episodes with Master, friends and villagers await!<br><br>- You can adjust the game to full screen with the F3 and F4 buttons,<br>  but Due to the nature of the game, it is recommended to play in windowed mode.<br>- Report bugs and typos in the game to <a href=\"mailto:hi.kkangto@gmail.com\">hi.kkangto@gmail.com</a>.<br><br><strong>F3 : Windowed background fill F4 : Full screen F5 : Reset game F12 : Screenshot</strong>",
